name: Alizee Jacotey (2000s)
description:
Alizée Lyonnet (née Jacotey) is a French singer who rose into stardom in the early 2000s.

Update: The TI has been updated after a 2-star review complaining about its oversaturation. Granted, version 1.0 was indeed oversaturated, but that was easily fixable by simply reducing the weight of the TI a little bit. Did it deserve a 2-star review just for that, basically ignoring any other merits? I very much doubt so, but to each their own, I guess. It's pushed me to create a new version of this TI, which was one of my first. It probably was about time anyway.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (alizjacot:0.99), a woman, RAW, close portrait photo, long brown coat, turtleneck sweater, pale skin, slim body, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3 sharp focus, f 5.6".
